name: Rumpis Kitchen
address: Jl. Dewi Madri IV No.6, Sumerta Kelod, Kec. Denpasar Tim., Kota Denpasar, Bali 80239, Indonesia
types: restaurant, coffee_shop, cafe, bakery, wholesaler, store, food
review 1:
I recently got a beautiful and delicious vegan lotus Biscoff Cake delivered in Bali for a birthday celebration.
The bakery was very patient and kind while communicating with me for my many different requests for the cake. The pricing is very reasonable for the quality of the vegan cake. The cake was so creamy, moist and delicious we were shocked it is vegan. i definitely would recommend anyone to come over to get any delicious beautiful pastries or cakes from Rumpis. I have tried many vegan pastries around Bali and i can safely say this is best tasting and looking vegan cake. They accommodate to many diets and offer vegan, gluten free or even refined sugar free cakes.

Thank you so much to the staff for helping make a beautiful cake and for being very nice and kind üòçüòç. I will definitely be back again to get more cakes!!!
review 2: I ordered gluten-free cupcakes for my daughter's 22nd birthday. All contact was via WhatsApp and so very helpful about all the options. I could not find what I wanted on the Instagram page for the cupcakes, so I sent what I wanted in terms of style and which colours and type of frosting. The cupcakes were a MASSIVE HIT. They exceeded our expectations and the birthday girl was very happy. We will be ordering again!!! The entire process from enquiry to ordering to delivery was very smooth.
review 3:
I recently organised, ordered and paid for a cake for my friends fortieth birthday with Runpis from Australia to be delivered to the restaurant we would be having dinner at for her birthday.
I cannot tell you how delightful, helpful and amazing the bakery was. They communicated with me the whole time, they were able to make a gluten free, dairy free and refined sugar free cake that not only accounted for all allergies but that tasted so incredibly good the birthday girl ate the whole cake in one day!
I cannot recommend them highly enough.
review 4:
Been renovated and it‚Äôs really nice. Recommended to try their Chicken Steak, nice seasoning and good mashed potato.
